    <abstract>
      <t>This document defines an EDNS0 OPTION-CODE for conveying the
	Key Tag(s) of DNSKEYs that a Validating Resolver will use to
	validate the anticpated response.</t>  
      <t>The Key Tag option code is optionally provided by resolvers
	to servers for purposes of data collection only.</t>
    </abstract>
